Valérie Mairesse https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Val%C3%A9rie_Mairesse 0 Valérie Mairesse (born 8 June 1955) is a French stage and film actress. She was nominated for the César Awards 1978 for Best Supporting Actress for her role in Repérages. Valérie_Mairesse ( born 8_June_1955 ) is a_French_stage_and_film_actress .
